                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="sharmrx18"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                            text="&lt;p>Join us on a typical day in the life of an AbbVie employee driving change around the clock. We drop in on Sherri Carter, an associate director in our operations group. Sherri oversees a building and team that manufactures critical medicine. All while she does her part to promote greater diversity and inclusion by mentoring and nurturing talent. &lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
                    </container>
